All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary Enum Summary 
    Class Description
    AudioPlayer
    AudioPlayer class inherits from Product class and implements methods from MultimediaControl interface.
    Controller
    Controller class connects and adds to databases and uses those databases to display info to FXML elements like tables, listviews and text areas for the main GUI application as well as button inputs for on action events.
    Employee
    Employee class is the blueprint for a new employee.
    Item
    Item interface sets up getters and setters for product id, name and manufacturer.
    ItemType
    ItemType enum contains possible item types and their respective two letter codes.
    Main
    Main class runs main GUI application.
    MonitorType
    Enum for types of monitors.
    MoviePlayer
    MoviePlayer class builds a product object of ItemType visual that inherits from Product and implements from MultimediaControl.
    MultimediaControl
    Interface for AudioPlayer and MoviePlayer that sets up methods.
    Product
    Product class is the blueprint for a product object.
    ProductionRecord
    Production Record class is the blueprint for productionRecord objects.
    Screen
    Screen class creates a blueprint of a screen for a MoviePlayer object and implements ScreenSpec interface.
    ScreenSpec
    Interface with getter methods for screen objects.
